node.text:
Before you blow up the comments with your hot take that “ReTeNtIoN dOeSnT wOrK” - the problem here isn’t that we don’t retain them necessarily (although sometimes it could be appropriate) but that we don’t do anything to actually catch them up. We have 8th graders functioning at a 4th grade level and no one seems to care. 🤷🏼‍♀️
.
.
.
.
